race.comment: MY PHAR LADY (14) improving mare expected to go on with it this time in. Drifted back from the low draw and got out late with an eye-catching third down the outside over 1400m at Randwick Kensington. Can race a little closer and gets her chance to run the mile out . KINGSTON CHARM (5) stalked the speed and took time to wind up when she got out late to finish a narrow second over 1600m at this track. In peak condition and looking for J Mac to weave his magic from the sticky gate. STARPHISTOCATED (6) underrated mare who returned with an encouraging on-pace fifth over 1400m at Randwick Kensington. Comes to hand quickly and proven at this level. CHARLEROI (4) smart on his day and comes here in peak condition fifth-up. Can push forward from the sticky gate and take a hand in the finish.
